hotspoints.title: Image de Ben Laden
hotspoints.description: Osama bin Laden (1957-2011) was a notorious terrorist and the founder of al-Qaeda. He orchestrated the September 11 attacks, changing the world's perception of terrorism. His death in 2011 marked a significant event in the global fight against extremism.
